{"tid":2312811,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"高質greek yogurt好難搵","createTime":"2020-12-05T09:28:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-05T12:42:57.000Z","uid":177089,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"da4b8621b28126cb247b22af49084c476b60f61c","tid":2312811,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T09:28:14.000Z","msg":"試過好多隻greek yogurt 好難先搵到啱心水<br />\n<br />\n低質yogurt高糖高脂唔好味<br />\n中質一係高糖低脂一係調返轉<br />\n高質要控制到糖脂水平得嚟又好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/potion.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/potion.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GRnAo5t.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGRnAo5t.jpg&h=a2e957e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最近試緊呢隻 糖5.3g 脂6.3g per 100g<br />\n又好食 650g 45蚊左右 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a03b04e7b8bd98f1cb17ff3c5fe9046e3b84ac48","tid":2312811,"uid":63311,"like":1,"dislike":25,"score":-24,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T09:29:22.000Z","msg":"咁貴 食蒙牛算 平平地又有營養"},{"pid":"f8ab57b11546f9139ab549f3300182fdfdde8e92","tid":2312811,"uid":4001,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T09:30:44.000Z","msg":"呢隻係greek style，唔同的"},{"pid":"4d17b74cf236abe2551e3dfb5a03241bd72476d1","tid":2312811,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T09:30:48.000Z","msg":"樓主rich <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e48b6b0f0a78a9acd099e6beb92e552ff68b2797","tid":2312811,"uid":133743,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T09:31:35.000Z","msg":"Greek style唔係Greek yogurt"},{"pid":"9f02e23271b717b10f88c26997b63da0e3f03f9f","tid":2312811,"uid":79117,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T09:32:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a4bdd311c88c530f1ea65bbc46abe9b981033