Z","msg":"Greek style唔係Greek yogurt"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T09:58:12.000Z","msg":"普通乳酪多數用低脂牛奶製成，有啲會用「基因改造」牛奶或加水，比較流質，鈣含量相對最低。<br />\n<br />\n希臘式乳酪通常用低脂牛奶，再加入其他牛奶元素、澱粉質或糖，模仿希臘乳酪好濃嘅質地。澱粉質同糖含量相對較高，而且冇益生菌。<br />\n<br />\n優質嘅希臘乳酪會用真正牛奶，蛋白質同鈣質含量相對最高，鈉含量最低。質地最杰身，飽肚感最強。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/potion.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/potion.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/potion.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bcf8e12d0581d7ba61bffe0f010d21c0b29bcda","tid":2312811,"uid":118146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"77c8c388ece358e322192f854abe93f1ba7a8801","tid":2312811,"uid":177089,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e48b6b0f0a78a9acd099e6beb92e552ff68b2797","tid":2312811,"uid":133743,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T09:31:35.000Z","msg":"Greek style唔係Greek yogurt"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T09:58:12.000Z","msg":"普通乳酪多數用低脂牛奶製成，有啲會用「基因改造」牛奶或加水，比較流質，鈣含量相對最低。<br />\n<br />\n希臘式乳酪通常用低脂牛奶，再加入其他牛奶元素、澱粉質或糖，模仿希臘乳酪好濃嘅質地。澱粉質同糖含量相對較高，而且冇益生菌。<br />\n<br />\n優質嘅希臘乳酪會用真正牛奶，蛋白質同鈣質含量相對最高，鈉含量最低。質地最杰身，飽肚感最強。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/potion.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/potion.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/potion.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T10:12:18.000Z","msg":"所以人地咪話你yeo valley嗰款唔係greek yogurt而係greek style囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e40a3304f4a47ebdde11b0d280b811eee4d7e990","tid":2312811,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4bcf8e12d0581d7ba61bffe0f010d21c0b29bcda","tid":2312811,"uid":118146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"77c8c388ece358e322192f854abe93f1ba7a8801","tid":2312811,"uid":177089,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e48b6b0f0a78a9acd099e6beb92e552ff68b2797","tid":2312811,"uid":133743,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy"